{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775876847146,"sessionID":"ses_28580b4d1ffeK0mAmYw8p10j2Z","part":{"id":"prt_d7a8235d10010S8a5Aw59evliB","messageID":"msg_d7a80e616001Q7v9fKmK0i7pcd","sessionID":"ses_28580b4d1ffeK0mAmYw8p10j2Z","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-18b3ae3b0bea4a63bdcf808dc98abd6d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md","content":"# Delta Specification — MetadataService 与数据模型\n\nAR: AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型\nModule: cmd/cli\nLanguage: Python\nSize: M\n\n---\n\n## Requirement: MetadataService 初始化\n\nThe system SHALL provide `MetadataService` as a service class for metadata file operations.\n\n### Scenario: 默认构造\n\n- **GIVEN** `MetadataService` is instantiated\n- **WHEN** no arguments are provided\n- **THEN** `verbose` SHALL default to `False`\n\n### Scenario: verbose 参数传入\n\n- **GIVEN** `MetadataService(verbose=True)` is instantiated\n- **WHEN** the instance is created\n- **THEN** `self.verbose` SHALL be `True`\n\n---\n\n## Requirement: AgentMetadata 数据模型 (Pydantic BaseModel)\n\nThe system SHALL define `AgentMetadata` as a Pydantic `BaseModel` with field validators for language, build_mode, and port.\n\n### Scenario: 必填字段验证\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` is instantiated\n- **WHEN** `agent_name` or `entrypoint` is not provided\n- **THEN** Pydantic SHALL raise `ValidationError` (fields marked with `Field(..., description=...)` are required)\n\n### Scenario: 可选字段默认值\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` is instantiated without optional fields\n- **WHEN** defaults are applied\n- **THEN** the following defaults SHALL be used:\n  - `description`: `\"\"`\n  - `language`: `\"python\"`\n  - `port`: `8080`\n  - `build_mode`: `\"local\"`\n  - `region`: `\"\"`\n  - `version`: `\"\"`\n  - `image`: `default_factory=dict` (empty dict)\n  - `auth`: `default_factory=dict` (empty dict)\n  - `requirements_file`: `\"requirements.txt\"`\n  - `registry_url`: `\"\"`\n  - `registry_username`: `\"\"`\n  - `registry_password`: `\"\"`\n  - `agent_endpoint`: `\"\"`\n  - `workload_manager_url`: `\"\"`\n  - `router_url`: `\"\"`\n  - `readiness_probe_path`: `\"\"`\n  - `readiness_probe_port`: `8080`\n  - `agent_id`: `\"\"`\n  - `session_id`: `\"\"`\n  - `k8s_deployment`: `default_factory=dict` (empty dict)\n\n### Scenario: language 字段验证 — 大写转换\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `language=\"Python\"` or `\"PYTHON\"`\n- **WHEN** the field validator runs\n- **THEN** the value SHALL be lowercased to `\"python\"` and accepted\n\n### Scenario: language 字段验证 — 非允许值拒绝\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `language=\"go\"` or `\"ruby\"`\n- **WHEN** the field validator runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError(\"language must be one of ['python', 'java']\")`\n\n### Scenario: build_mode 字段验证 — 大写转换\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `build_mode=\"Local\"` or `\"LOCAL\"`\n- **WHEN** the field validator runs\n- **THEN** the value SHALL be lowercased to `\"local\"` and accepted\n\n### Scenario: build_mode 字段验证 — 非允许值拒绝\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `build_mode=\"docker\"` or `\"remote\"`\n- **WHEN** the field validator runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError(\"build_mode must be one of ['local', 'cloud']\")`\n\n### Scenario: port 字段验证 — 有效范围\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `port=8080` or `port=1` or `port=65535`\n- **WHEN** the field validator runs\n- **THEN** the value SHALL be accepted\n\n### Scenario: port 字段验证 — 超出范围拒绝\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `port=0` or `port=65536` or `port=-1`\n- **WHEN** the field validator runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError(\"port must be between 1 and 65535\")`\n\n---\n\n## Requirement: MetadataService.load_metadata\n\nThe system SHALL load metadata from YAML files with primary filename `agent_metadata.yaml` and fallback order: `agent.yaml`, `metadata.yaml`.\n\n### Scenario: 主文件存在\n\n- **GIVEN** `{workspace_path}/agent_metadata.yaml` exists\n- **WHEN** `load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\n- **THEN** the system SHALL:\n  - Read the file content with `yaml.safe_load`\n  - Construct `AgentMetadata(**data)` from parsed YAML\n  - Return the `AgentMetadata` instance\n\n### Scenario: 主文件不存在 — 回退到 agent.yaml\n\n- **GIVEN** `agent_metadata.yaml` does NOT exist but `agent.yaml` exists\n- **WHEN** `load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\n- **THEN** the system SHALL load from `agent.yaml` and return `AgentMetadata`\n\n### Scenario: 主和次级文件不存在 — 回退到 metadata.yaml\n\n- **GIVEN** `agent_metadata.yaml` and `agent.yaml` do NOT exist but `metadata.yaml` exists\n- **WHEN** `load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\n- **THEN** the system SHALL load from `metadata.yaml` and return `AgentMetadata`\n\n### Scenario: 所有元数据文件不存在\n\n- **GIVEN** none of `agent_metadata.yaml`, `agent.yaml`, `metadata.yaml` exist in workspace\n- **WHEN** `load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise `FileNotFoundError(\"No metadata file found in workspace: {workspace_path}\")`\n\n### Scenario: YAML 内容为空或 null\n\n- **GIVEN** the metadata file exists but content is empty or YAML parses to `None`\n- **WHEN** the file is loaded\n- **THEN** the system SHALL treat empty content as `{}` and create `AgentMetadata` with defaults\n\n### Scenario: YAML 内容字段类型错误\n\n- **GIVEN** metadata YAML contains `port: \"not-a-number\"` (invalid type)\n- **WHEN** `AgentMetadata(**data)` validation runs\n- **THEN** Pydantic SHALL raise `ValidationError` for the type mismatch\n\n---\n\n## Requirement: MetadataService.save_metadata\n\nThe system SHALL persist metadata to `{workspace_path}/agent_metadata.yaml` using `yaml.dump` with specific formatting options.\n\n### Scenario: 保存到主文件路径\n\n- **GIVEN** `workspace_path` exists and `metadata` is an `AgentMetadata` instance\n- **WHEN** `save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)` is called\n- **THEN** the system SHALL:\n  - Write to `{workspace_path}/agent_metadata.yaml`\n  - Return the file `Path` object\n\n### Scenario: YAML 输出格式参数\n\n- **GIVEN** metadata is being saved\n- **WHEN** `yaml.dump` is called\n- **THEN** the following parameters SHALL be used:\n  - `default_flow_style=False` (block format, not inline)\n  - `indent=2`\n  - `sort_keys=False` (preserve field order)\n  - Data from `metadata.model_dump(exclude_none=True)` (exclude `None` fields)\n\n### Scenario: 空字典字段包含在输出\n\n- **GIVEN** `image`, `auth`, or `k8s_deployment` fields are empty dicts `{}` (not `None`)\n- **WHEN** metadata is saved\n- **THEN** empty dicts SHALL be included in YAML output (because `exclude_none=True` only excludes `None`, not empty dicts)\n\n### Scenario: None 值字段排除\n\n- **GIVEN** a field value is `None` (not an empty string or empty dict)\n- **WHEN** metadata is saved with `exclude_none=True`\n- **THEN** that field SHALL NOT appear in the YAML output\n\n---\n\n## Requirement: MetadataService.update_metadata (待实现)\n\nThe system SHALL provide `update_metadata` to load existing metadata, apply updates, and save.\n\n### Scenario: 更新部分字段\n\n- **GIVEN** workspace has existing metadata file with `version=\"\"` and `description=\"old\"`\n- **WHEN** `update_metadata(workspace_path, {\"version\": \"v1.0.0\", \"description\": \"new desc\"})` is called\n- **THEN** the system SHALL:\n  - Load existing metadata via `load_metadata`\n  - Apply the updates dict to metadata fields\n  - Save via `save_metadata`\n  - Return the updated `AgentMetadata` instance\n\n### Scenario: 更新触发验证错误\n\n- **GIVEN** updates dict contains `{\"language\": \"rust\"}`\n- **WHEN** the updated metadata is validated\n- **THEN** `AgentMetadata` validator SHALL raise `ValueError` for invalid language\n\n---\n\n## Requirement: MetadataService.validate_workspace (待实现)\n\nThe system SHALL validate workspace structure based on the language specified in metadata.\n\n### Scenario: workspace 路径不存在\n\n- **GIVEN** `workspace_path` does NOT exist or is NOT a directory\n- **WHEN** `validate_workspace(workspace_path)` is called\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError` with message indicating path does not exist or is not a directory\n\n### Scenario: Python workspace 验证成功\n\n- **GIVEN** metadata `language == \"python\"` and workspace contains at least one `.py` file\n- **WHEN** `_validate_python_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)` runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL return without raising an error\n\n### Scenario: Python workspace 无 Python 文件\n\n- **GIVEN** metadata `language == \"python\"` and workspace has NO `.py` files\n- **WHEN** `_validate_python_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)` runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace\")`\n\n### Scenario: Java workspace 验证成功\n\n- **GIVEN** metadata `language == \"java\"` and workspace contains `pom.xml`\n- **WHEN** `_validate_java_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)` runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL return without raising an error\n\n### Scenario: Java workspace 无 pom.xml\n\n- **GIVEN** metadata `language == \"java\"` and workspace has NO `pom.xml`\n- **WHEN** `_validate_java_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)` runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError(\"pom.xml not found in workspace\")`\n\n---\n\n## Requirement: MetadataOptions 数据类 (pack_models.py)\n\nThe system SHALL define `MetadataOptions` as a dataclass for CLI option mapping.\n\n### Scenario: 默认值设置\n\n- **GIVEN** `MetadataOptions` is instantiated without arguments\n- **WHEN** defaults are applied\n- **THEN** the following defaults SHALL be used:\n  - `agent_name`: `None`\n  - `language`: `\"python\"`\n  - `entrypoint`: `None`\n  - `port`: `8080`\n  - `build_mode`: `\"local\"`\n  - `requirements_file`: `None`\n  - `description`: `None`\n  - `workload_manager_url`: `\"\"`\n  - `router_url`: `\"\"`\n  - `readiness_probe_path`: `\"\"`\n  - `readiness_probe_port`: `8080`\n  - `registry_url`: `\"\"`\n  - `registry_username`: `\"\"`\n  - `registry_password`: `\"\"`\n  - `agent_endpoint`: `\"\"`\n\n### Scenario: from_options 工厂方法 — 正常输入\n\n- **GIVEN** `options = {\"agent_name\": \"my-agent\", \"language\": \"java\", \"port\": 9090}`\n- **WHEN** `MetadataOptions.from_options(options)` is called\n- **THEN** the system SHALL:\n  - Filter out entries where value is `None`\n  - Create `MetadataOptions` instance with remaining values\n  - Return instance with `agent_name=\"my-agent\"`, `language=\"java\"`, `port=9090`\n\n### Scenario: from_options 工厂方法 — 过滤 None 值\n\n- **GIVEN** `options = {\"agent_name\": None, \"language\": \"python\", \"entrypoint\": None}`\n- **WHEN** `MetadataOptions.from_options(options)` is called\n- **THEN** the system SHALL:\n  - Filter out `\"agent_name\"` and `\"entrypoint\"` because their values are `None`\n  - Return instance using defaults for filtered fields\n\n### Scenario: from_options 工厂方法 — 未知键忽略\n\n- **GIVEN** `options = {\"agent_name\": \"test\", \"unknown_field\": \"value\"}`\n- **WHEN** `MetadataOptions.from_options(options)` is called\n- **THEN** the system SHALL:\n  - Pass only matching dataclass fields to constructor\n  - Ignore `unknown_field` or raise error depending on implementation\n\n---\n\n## Requirement: Metadata 文件格式规范\n\nThe system SHALL use YAML format with specific naming and formatting conventions.\n\n### Scenario: 主文件名 agent_metadata.yaml\n\n- **GIVEN** metadata is saved\n- **WHEN** `MetadataService.save_metadata` runs\n- **THEN** the primary filename SHALL be `agent_metadata.yaml` (not `agentcube.yaml`)\n\n### Scenario: 加载文件名优先级\n\n- **GIVEN** multiple metadata files may exist\n- **WHEN** `MetadataService.load_metadata` searches for files\n- **THEN** the priority order SHALL be:\n  1. `agent_metadata.yaml` (primary)\n  2. `agent.yaml` (fallback)\n  3. `metadata.yaml` (secondary fallback)\n\n---\n\n## Requirement: Pydantic validator 使用 field_validator\n\nThe system SHALL use Pydantic v2 `field_validator` decorator for field validation.\n\n### Scenario: validator 方法签名\n\n- **GIVEN** a field validator is defined\n- **WHEN** using `@field_validator(\"language\")`\n- **THEN** the validator method SHALL be a `@classmethod` and receive `v: str` (the field value)\n\n### Scenario: validator 返回转换值\n\n- **GIVEN** `language` validator lowercases the input\n- **WHEN** input is `\"Python\"`\n- **THEN** validator SHALL return `\"python\"` (the transformed value)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata` model, `MetadataService` class |\n| `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `pydantic>=2.0.0` | `BaseModel`, `Field`, `field_validator` |\n| `pyyaml>=6.0` | `yaml.safe_load`, `yaml.dump` |\n| `pathlib` | `Path` for file operations |\n\n---\n\n## Validation Checklist\n\n- [ ] `AgentMetadata` defined as Pydantic `BaseModel`\n- [ ] Required fields: `agent_name`, `entrypoint` (use `Field(...)`)\n- [ ] Optional fields have correct defaults (`\"\"`, `default_factory=dict`, etc.)\n- [ ] `validate_language` accepts `python`/`java`, lowercases input, rejects others\n- [ ] `validate_build_mode` accepts `local`/`cloud`, lowercases input, rejects others\n- [ ] `validate_port` accepts `1..65535`, rejects out-of-range\n- [ ] `MetadataService.__init__` accepts `verbose` parameter\n- [ ] `load_metadata` checks `agent_metadata.yaml` first, then `agent.yaml`, then `metadata.yaml`\n- [ ] `load_metadata` raises `FileNotFoundError` when no file found\n- [ ] `load_metadata` handles empty YAML as `{}` with defaults\n- [ ] `save_metadata` writes to `agent_metadata.yaml`\n- [ ] `save_metadata` uses `yaml.dump(default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False)`\n- [ ] `save_metadata` uses `model_dump(exclude_none=True)`\n- [ ] `save_metadata` returns `Path` to saved file\n- [ ] `MetadataOptions` dataclass with correct fields and defaults\n- [ ] `MetadataOptions.from_options` filters `None` values from input dict"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775876847074,"end":1775876847143}}}}
